Опис вакансії
I`m seeking for an energetic sales representative to join our successful e-commerce project. If you are looking for a fulfilling, fast paced opportunity and your main passion is money — welcome aboard!Responsibilities:• Outgoing line with HOT client base (NO COLD CALLS AT ALL)• Follow up with customers by phone, email and other methods in order to close/repeat the sale• Deliver the most positive experience to make sure the customer is satisfied and he comes back soon to fulfill his product needsRequirements:• C1 level of English is a MUST!• Successful previous experience as a sales manager, consistently meeting or exceeding targets (will be a plus)• Demonstrated ability to communicate, present and influence credibly and effectively• Proven ability to drive the sales processOur conditions:• Base salary — starts from $500 + great BONUSES + % (payed on time, no delays); Avarage paycheck starts with $2000• Full training (paid by our company)• A comfortable office in Kiev downtown (convenient transportation, modern working conditions)• Career ladder: from trainee to Head of Sales. We do not hire management, we develop our staff.
